World Cup winners
Three players have won the FIFA World Cup whilst FC Barcelona players:
Maradona (MEX 1986)
Romário (USA 1994)
Rivaldo (Korea-Japan 2002)
European Championship winners
Six players have won the European Championship whilst at FC Barcelona, all with Spain:
Jesús María Pereda (1964)
Josep Fusté (1964)
Fernando Olivella (1964)
Carles Puyol (2008)
Xavi (2008)
Andrés Iniesta (2008)
